@startuml Admin_SystemConfiguration

title Admin - System Configuration (Module B)

actor Admin as "🔐 Admin"

rectangle "INDUSTRIES" {
    usecase "List All\nIndustries" as B9
    usecase "Create Industry" as B10
    usecase "Update Industry" as B9_1
    usecase "Delete Industry" as B9_2
}

rectangle "LOCATIONS" {
    usecase "List All\nLocations" as B11
    usecase "Create Location" as B12
    usecase "Update Location" as B11_1
    usecase "Delete Location" as B11_2
}

Admin --> B9: 1. List industries
B9 --> B10: 2. Create
B9 --> B9_1: 3. Update
B9 --> B9_2: 4. Delete

Admin --> B11: 5. List locations
B11 --> B12: 6. Create
B11 --> B11_1: 7. Update
B11 --> B11_2: 8. Delete

note right of B9
  **Priority:** P1 (Important)
  **Status:** Need Validation
end note

@enduml
